===Boss Phases===
Several bosses have multiple phases:

'''Metal Mantis:'''
* Phase 1: Standard attacks, 100% HP
* Phase 2: Faster attacks, <50% HP

'''Deathtoll:'''
* Phase 1: Human form (HP 200)
* Phase 2: Demon form (HP 300)
* Uses magic attacks in both phases

